snippet.title: Lofi Hip Hop Worlds To Study In - Gameplay
snippet.description:
LoFi Hip Hop Worlds To Study In is a game full of unique study spots with Lofi Hip Hop music and ASMR sounds.  

You can explore the game to relax while you take a break from studying. 

When it's time to study again, you can set a timer in the game, and put its worlds in the background. To help you focus, they will continue to provide relaxing sounds and beats with no ads. 

In these worlds, nothing is trying to hurt you.  You don't need to fight anything to win.  You set your own goals, and you can customize your own soundscape to help you meet them.
